    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Clothes presses flanked with additional drawers and storage areas on either side of the central carcass, coined in the late 18th and early 19th centuries.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000046362/Sotheby's Online (2001-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Término de época empleado a fines del siglo XVIII y principios del siglo XIX para describir armarios de ropa con cajones adicionales y áreas de almacenamiento a cada lado de un cuerpo central.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Historische benaming die eind 18e en begin 19e eeuw werd gebruikt voor 'clothes presses' met extra laden en opbergruimtes aan beide zijdes van het middengedeelte.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>衣櫃兩邊側面有額外的抽屜，中間部分則每邊都有儲藏空間，製造於十八世紀晚期和十九世紀早期。</Note_Text>
